channel.title: Insane-f2pk COMING BACK SOON V3
channel.description:
I have been working on a version 3 for quite some time now, I have decided to take the server down last month until I am done with updates. I had a poor host which gave me alot of down time, when the server was not down the community seemed to have alot of fun. I'd like to thank Adam and Chase for their fine previous work and teaching of coding in v1 and v2. I have not had help yet in the v3 trying to get all the coding knowledge I can. When I first released the server, it was my first private server ever, I should not have released yet but I needed it tested to find out the flaws. I have been going through the insane-f2pk forums and have taken alot of suggestions into consideration implying them into the game. Server now has a webclient ready and will be hosted on a dedi when i release v3. Do not forget about me my fellow players :) I will not let you down, major updating has commenced! You can find my on msn or sometimes I log in king-pk IGN insane pk3r.
Ps. chase I have not forgot about you times are rough, I will get to you asap. THANKS!
